---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="The Future of Web Development: Why Shelby Businesses Need Modern Websites Now"
  description="Explore the latest web development trends and why staying modern is essential for Shelby, NC businesses in 2026."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-cyan/20 bg-brand-cyan/5">
          <span class="text-brand-cyan text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #2 Article #10</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/30"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-sky/60 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">June 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          The Future of Web Development: <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan to-brand-blue">Why Shelby Businesses Need Modern Sites Now</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          The way customers find and choose local services has changed dramatically. If your website was built before 2022, it's likely costing you money. Professional web development is no longer optional — it's essential.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-3xl mb-16 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/20 to-transparent opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
           <span class="text-brand-sky/20 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transform -rotate-12">Shelby Web Company Official</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-sky/90 mb-12">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline decoration-brand-cyan/30 underline-offset-4">Shelby Web Company</a> helps Shelby and surrounding area businesses stay ahead with modern, conversion-focused websites.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">01.</span> Key Web Development Trends Every Local Business Should Know
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Mobile-First & Speed Optimized</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Most "web designers near me" searches happen on phones. Slow sites lose visitors instantly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">AI-Powered Lead Tools</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Smart chat, instant quote forms, and automated follow-ups are no longer just for big corporations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Strong Local SEO Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Built-in optimization so you rank for your services + location automatically.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Seamless User Experience</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Clear navigation, fast booking, and trust-building elements that turn visitors into clients.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-blue/5 border-l-4 border-brand-blue p-8 my-12 rounded-r-2xl">
          <p class="text-white font-medium italic mb-0">"Our web design Shelby team builds all of these features into every project, customized for your industry."</p>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm mt-4 mb-0">— Shelby Web Company Philosophy</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">02.</span> Deep Dive: AI and Core Web Vitals in 2026
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">AI That Sells</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 mb-0">
              AI isn't just for bots anymore. In 2026, we're using predictive AI to track how users move their mice and scroll. If a visitor looks like they're about to leave, we can trigger a high-value "exit offer" specifically for Shelby locals.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The 1-Second Rule</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 mb-0">
              Google's "Core Web Vitals" now prioritize Largest Contentful Paint (LCP) more than ever. If your site takes more than 1.5 seconds to feel "active," you will lose 40% of your Shelby traffic to competitors. Our web development process guarantees high-speed scores.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">03.</span> Why Partner with a Local SEO Agency Shelby
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">
          A beautiful website means nothing if no one sees it. That's why we combine expert web development with proven local SEO strategies. We help you dominate searches like "plumber Shelby NC," "roofer near me," and more.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8">Don't Get Left Behind</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-12">Businesses that upgrade their online presence in 2026 are seeing:</p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-24">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/30 border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-brand-accent text-2xl">✓</span>
            <span class="text-white font-bold">More phone calls</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/30 border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-brand-accent text-2xl">✓</span>
            <span class="text-white font-bold">Higher quote request volume</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/30 border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-brand-accent text-2xl">✓</span>
            <span class="text-white font-bold">Better brand trust</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/30 border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-brand-accent text-2xl">✓</span>
            <span class="text-white font-bold">Increased revenue</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-dark p-12 rounded-[2rem] text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(132,204,22,0.1),transparent_70%)]"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 relative z-10">Ready to Future-Proof Your Business?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            If you're ready for a website that works as hard as you do, reach out to the top web designers near me in the Shelby area.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-glow-shine bg-brand-accent text-[#0A0A0A] px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-accent-light">
              Get Started Today
            </a>
            <a href="tel:7044738188" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
              (704) 473-8188
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-8 relative z-10">
             Special Offer: Free logo design with every new web project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer navigation -->
      <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/services/web-design" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Web Design</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
